The paper deals with the synthesis of strategies in network systems with active cyber deception, which involves game theory, security, artificial intelligence, and systems engineering. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.GT (Computer Science and Game Theory), followed by cs.CR (Computer Science and Cryptography), cs.AI (Computer Science and Artificial Intelligence), cs.SY (Computer Science and Systems), and cs.SE (Computer Science and Software Engineering).
